{
  "texts": [
    "The ReRAM crossbars store the pre-trained weights on-chip, which are spatially distributed across ReRAM cores.",
    "The resulting activations flow from the 𝑖 𝑡ℎ layer to the (𝑖 + 1) 𝑡ℎ layer in a unidirectional manner across ReRAM cores.",
    "If two consecutive transformer layers are mapped far apart, it will lead to longrange multi-hop communication.",
    "This, in turn, will degrade the performance and energy efficiency of the NoC.",
    "Therefore, it is essential to ensure continuity in the ReRAM core placement to the extent possible to reduce communication overhead."
  ]
}